1. 如何面对
[Dm] Ru he mian dui 
曾一起走过的日子
Zeng [Gm] yi qi zou guo de ri zi
现在剩下我独行
[C] Xian zai sheng xia wo du [Am] xing
如何让心声一一讲你知
Ru he rang [Dm] xin sheng yi yi jiang ni zhi

从来无人明白我
[Dm] Cong lai wu ren ming bai wo
唯一你给我好日子
Wei [Gm] yi ni gei wo hao ri zi
有你有我有情有生有死有义
[C] You ni you wo you qing you sheng you si you [F] yi [A7]

多少风波都愿闯
[Dm] Duo shao feng bo du yuan chuang
只因彼此不死的目光
Zhi yin [Gm] bi ci bu si de mu guang
有你有我有情有天有海有地
[C] You ni you wo you qing you tian you hai you [F] di [A7]

不可猜测总有天意
[Dm] Bu ke cai ce zong you tian yi
才珍惜相处的日子
Cai [Gm] zhen xi xiang chu de ri zi
道别话亦未多讲
[Am] Dao bie hua yi wei duo jiang
只抛低这个伤心的汉子
Zhi pao di [Dm] zhe ge shang xin de han zi

2. 沉沉睡了
[Dm] Chen chen shui liao 
谁分享今生的日子
Shui [Gm] fen xiang jin sheng de ri zi
活着但是没灵魂
[C] Huo zhuo dan shi mei ling [Am] hun
才明白生死之间的意思
Cai ming bai [Dm] sheng si zhi jian de yi si

情浓完全明白了
[Dm] Qing nong wan quan ming bai liao
才甘心披上孤独衣
Cai [Gm] gan xin pi shang gu du yi
有你有我有情有天有海有地
[C] You ni you wo you qing you tian you hai you [F] di [A7] 

当天一起不自知
[Dm] Dang tian yi qi bu zi zhi
分开方知根本心极痴
Fen kai [Gm] fang zhi gen ben xin ji chi
有你有我有情有生有死有义
[C] You ni you wo you qing you sheng you si you [F] yi [A7] 

只想解释当我不智
[Dm] Zhi xiang jie shi dang wo bu zhi
如今想倾诉讲谁知
Ru [Gm] jin xiang qing su jiang shui zhi
剩下绝望旧身影
[Am] Sheng xia jue wang jiu shen ying
今只得千亿伤心的句子
Jin zhi de [Dm] qian yi shang xin de ju zi

